text:
[Verse]
Tick tock goes the clock
Feel the beat never stop
Turn it up let it drop
Hearts racing flip flop

[Verse 2]
Blast from the past it’s here
Memories loud and clear
Fade away don’t appear
Let’s dance shake off fear

[Chorus]
Dancing through time we go
Step by step rhythm flow
Fast forward nice and slow
Let your spirit start to glow

[Verse 3]
Night sky stars in line
Feel the pulse it’s divine
Hold my hand you’re mine
Together we’ll intertwine

[Chorus]
Dancing through time we go
Step by step rhythm flow
Fast forward nice and slow
Let your spirit start to glow

[Bridge]
Every move every sway
Dreams in the moonlight play
Here we are night or day
Let’s dance
Come what may
title: Dancing Through Time
